Dialogue: 1,0:00:05.02,0:00:07.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(40,0)}{\c&HA0A0A0&}This story is fiction. The names of people,\Nplaces and groups are imaginary.\NObey traffic rules and drive safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:38.18,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Kogoeta machi ni giniro shita kemuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.18,0:00:41.88,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,...misugita yume no daisyou.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.88,0:00:45.61,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Kogoeta karada furikirenai omoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.61,0:00:49.28,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Accel funde gomakasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.28,0:00:56.64,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoru ni kowareta mama shisen tsuyoku togarasete.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.64,0:01:04.03,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Dareno kimagure kara sekai sae mo owarisoude.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.03,0:01:05.98,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,"Break in 2 the nite" It's that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.98,0:01:09.56,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Obieta me wo shite lost in the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.56,0:01:13.22,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Ochiteku yume ni dakareru.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.22,0:01:16.98,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Kodoku ga kowakute missin' my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.98,0:01:20.69,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Jibun sae mo kizu tsukete.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.69,0:01:24.37,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Taoreru kurai ni love me so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.37,0:01:28.06,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,Subete wo suttee anata wo...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.06,0:01:31.72,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,...ai suru koto sae dekitara...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.72,0:01:35.96,Song,,0000,0000,0000,,...kitto sunao ni naresou.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.59,0:01:56.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a good cure to save\NTakumi from his lovesickness?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.67,0:02:04.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's Friday, so September 15th\Nis still a week away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:07.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We're lucky that it's not tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.82,0:02:13.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, there's a race between the\NRedsuns and the Myogi Night Kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.41,0:02:14.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:19.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll drag Takumi out there,\Nand watch the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:23.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be stimulated and recover!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:27.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good idea!\NThat's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.14,0:02:32.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll knock him out and save him\Nfrom his lovesickness.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:36.40,0:02:42.28,MainStyle,,0000,0060,0160,,{\fad(1000,1000)}{\2a&HFF&}Severe Hill Climb
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.05,0:02:56.24,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dad, I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:57.86,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.86,0:03:02.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I... drove on Mt. Usui the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.41,0:03:06.64,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,At first, I thought Usui was\Ntotally different from Akina.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:13.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But... I don't know\Nhow to say this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:16.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,They seemed almost the same\Nafter I started driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:20.59,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:21.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,"Well done?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:25.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Akina and Usui are totally different...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:28.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you simply drove in the same manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:34.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You tried what you do on Akina\Nin a different place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:37.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, take care of the delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:38.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:03.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Try what I do on Akina\Nin other places...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:15.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I know what you meant to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.01,0:04:16.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.45,0:04:35.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better take a nap when I get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:39.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takumi looks totally bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.19,0:04:42.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, it's the time to proceed\Nwith the plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:45.11,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takumi!\NTakumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:49.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, big news!\NDon't be surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:53.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The Redsuns and Night Kids are racing!\NAnd it's tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:54.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.81,0:04:57.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me "wha," will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.82,0:05:00.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're racing against Takahashi\NRyosuke next week...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:02.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...so you shouldn't miss this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:04.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:06.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, we've decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:09.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,And it'd be a waste of gas\Nto go in two cars...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:11.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...so we'll go in your Eight-Six?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.54,0:05:12.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:14.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:17.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you excited?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:22.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be at the usual place at\Nseven o'clock tonight...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.18,0:05:25.24,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...so make sure you borrow\Nthe Eight-Six, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:44.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, there're so many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.66,0:05:46.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen Takumi and Itsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.83,0:05:48.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No.  I guess they aren't here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:53.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I let Itsuki handle it, but I'm worried\Nif they'll make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.31,0:05:57.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, Takumi?\NIt's gonna start soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.84,0:06:02.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you didn't want to take\Nthe highway, we got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:04.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so stingy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.50,0:06:05.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:09.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to save gas and\Ndidn't drive your Eight-Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:13.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I've never heard of a Road Racer\Nwho's bad at directions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:18.52,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}It must be because of a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.52,0:06:19.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:23.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, we don't have much time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.37,0:06:38.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:42.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The hero always arrives late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:44.88,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Myogi's valley is deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.88,0:06:47.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better be concerned\Nabout your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:51.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Can it.  Aren't you shaking from fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.02,0:06:52.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll defeat you so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.68,0:06:55.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No one in the Night Kids can match me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:59.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope your overconfidence\Ndoesn't kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:06.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better start before\Nthe rain comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:07.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:10.43,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The Eight-Six!\NIt's Akina's Eight-Six!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:14.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The Eight-Six?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.39,0:07:26.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, look at all the people\Nin the galleries...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:29.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,First, let's find those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.70,0:07:34.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.  Since there are\Nso many people, it's tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:37.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Where should we park the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.63,0:07:41.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we go to the peak?\NThere's a big parking lot there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.32,0:07:43.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.  I'll head for the peak for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:53.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}So he's come after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.18,0:07:55.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}It excites me whether\NI like it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:56.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Eight-Six...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:08:00.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...I'll show you how much\NI've improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.09,0:08:05.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Eight-Six!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.26,0:08:06.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,From Akina?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:08.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:09.49,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So, that's the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.93,0:08:13.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takumi, I noticed earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.08,0:08:16.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think they're watching us?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.69,0:08:17.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:22.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dunno...?"\NWe really stand out...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.32,0:08:25.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...because Akina's Eight-Six is famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.99,0:08:29.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone thinks so highly of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:32.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I was right about coming\Nin the Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.41,0:08:34.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.79,0:08:37.17,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:38.27,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:40.39,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.56,0:08:51.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.\NNo oncoming traffic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.59,0:08:53.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting the countdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.02,0:08:54.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Five...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.31,0:08:55.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...four...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:56.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...three...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:57.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...two...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:08:58.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:08:59.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.82,0:09:11.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What an incredible rocket start!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:15.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Keisuke'll win.\NI know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.12,0:09:20.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Don't lose.  We can't disgrace ourselves\Nby losing on our home course.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:23.46,0:09:24.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0130,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Takahashi
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:28.24,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:33.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:38.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The FD's greatest advantage\Nis its manueverability.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:40.61,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Don't forget that, Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:50.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takumi, don't you think Myogi's\Npasses are similar to Akina's?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:52.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.08,0:09:55.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say that they remind me of Usui.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.25,0:09:58.22,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!  They're nothing like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:10:02.77,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}It's no use.  His sickness is deeper\Nthan the Marianas Trench.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:06.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, Takumi, look carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:12.85,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as narrow as Usui, and this dynamic\Nclimbing path is very similar to Akina's.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.85,0:10:16.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I mean.\NThe rhythm is similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.60,0:10:18.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,"R...rhythm?"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.65,0:10:47.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He's tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.94,0:10:50.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The FD's fast in the corners.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.01,0:10:55.21,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I didn't expect anyone to keep up\Nwith my R and I on Myogi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:02.20,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}He's started steering hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.20,0:11:04.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Is he going to increase the pace\Nto try and outrun me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:08.92,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}If you do that on the downhill, the tires\Nwill definitely lose grip.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.33,0:12:02.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This's the midpoint, and\Nthey just went past.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.18,0:12:06.67,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}The 32 is ahead, but\Nthe gap is minimal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.67,0:12:08.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:10.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.07,0:12:14.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Nakazato pulling away from\NKeisuke at the corner's exit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.06,0:12:20.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Well, he's slightly slower at the exit,\Nbut he's keeping up overall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.02,0:12:21.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}His driving is very smooth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.89,0:12:26.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}It's very different from\NNakazato's drastic driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.82,0:12:29.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I got it.\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.03,0:12:35.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}If you're doing that, you've\Nimproved, Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.22,0:12:39.24,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}The R32 is ahead, but there's\Nno gap in between.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.12,0:12:41.61,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}They just passed us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.61,0:12:45.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}The 32 is ahead, but the\NFD is right behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.08,0:12:47.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Takeshi seems to be doing alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.98,0:12:50.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been practicing so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.44,0:12:53.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's been totally different since\Nhe was defeated by Akina's Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:13:01.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I've considered him my enemy even though\Nwe're on the same team, but now...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.47,0:13:07.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}...when I think about him driving\Nfor our pride, my chest aches.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.74,0:13:10.11,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I've never had a feeling like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:14.16,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Here comes the 32.\NThe FD's right behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.59,0:13:17.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Please win, Takeshi!\NI'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.73,0:13:26.32,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only hear the sounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:28.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,They're taking so long to get up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.59,0:13:30.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.23,0:13:32.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.70,0:13:39.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad.  It's in the middle\Nof an attack at max speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:42.35,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The beginning of a rainstorm\Nis the most dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.35,0:13:45.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The dust and sand on the asphalt\Nare stirred up by the rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:47.29,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...and the road'll be extremely slippery.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:49.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You can lose grip very suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.03,0:14:02.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}It's started raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.06,0:14:04.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Damn, the goal is so close...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.75,0:14:07.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}The beginning of the rain\Nis most dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:10.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}When you skid, it happens\Nwithout any warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.68,0:14:47.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting heavier.\NI hope it won't be canceled.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:49.71,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Itsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.63,0:14:55.42,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...the goal is over there, which means\Nthis is the last corner, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.93,0:15:03.96,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Myogi's peak, so this short section just\Nbefore the goal is slightly downhill, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.96,0:15:06.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the last part is downhill...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.77,0:15:08.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.46,0:15:33.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Now it's time to settle this match!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:36.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}Impossible!  You won't be able\Nto turn at that speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.97,0:15:39.44,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}That idiot's gonna crash\Ninto the cliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.73,0:15:49.05,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I can do it.\NI have feedback. {a feeling}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:51.75,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}My FD's telling me to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.82,0:16:01.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming this way!  Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:26.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Goal!\NThe FD won!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.97,0:16:34.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!  It's so awesome!\NTakahashi Keisuke is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.36,0:16:37.76,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}This is the first time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.76,0:16:41.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I've never been excited by watching\Nsomeone else race before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:46.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}I can't stand still after watching\Nsomething as incredible as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.75,0:16:54.09,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You were lucky, Takahashi Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:56.55,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No.  It was because of my skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:16:57.47,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.47,0:17:00.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The last corner was downhill...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:05.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...so I knew that the key would\Nbe the front tires' condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.07,0:17:10.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you wear down your tires, so the\Nfeedback from the front felt sluggish?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:15.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I saved my tires while\NI kept pace with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:17.63,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the difference in our abilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:38.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Keisuke, that's just like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:40.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do about the downhill?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.66,0:17:43.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to cancel it because of\Nthis heavy rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.41,0:17:44.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.13,0:17:48.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Keisuke, let me race\Nagainst Akina's Eight-Six!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.50,0:17:48.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:51.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay since it's not\Nour home course...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.53,0:17:55.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...and this isn't his home course either,\Nso the conditions are equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.36,0:17:55.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.98,0:17:56.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.94,0:17:58.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.74,0:17:59.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.66,0:18:01.68,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenta...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:06.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Fujiwara Takumi, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:10.30,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Nakamura Kenta of the Redsuns.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.30,0:18:13.60,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say?  Will you accept\Nmy challenge to a rain battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.60,0:18:16.23,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kenta, without checking\Nwith my brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.23,0:18:19.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's ask the galleries, Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.10,0:18:22.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, do you want to see a rain battle\Nbetween me and the Eight-Six?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.18,0:18:25.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.53,0:18:28.18,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.18,0:18:29.70,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,T...this is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.70,0:18:31.81,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He can't say no in this situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:36.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,B...but Takumi has a battle against\NTakahashi Ryosuke next week!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.48,0:18:38.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll race you first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.08,0:18:43.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If you lose to me, you don't deserve\Nto race against Ryosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.73,0:18:45.78,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just stand there.\NSay something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.78,0:18:48.53,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm confident driving in the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.53,0:18:51.76,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're scared\Nof the rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:55.28,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,N...no, the timing's bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.28,0:18:58.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,He's... not in the right mood...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.38,0:19:00.36,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:08.84,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,W...wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.84,0:19:11.73,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can stop them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:12.72,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.72,0:19:16.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The Eight-Six isn't only our target.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.26,0:19:20.07,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,All Road Racers want to race\Nagainst the Eight-Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.07,0:19:22.90,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand that, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.19,0:19:26.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:30.61,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to the downhill in the rain,\Nwe can compare our techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.61,0:19:34.45,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Go get your Eight-Six,\Nand pull up next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.43,0:19:36.48,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me, Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:38.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I riding with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:43.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If I leave you here, I'll have to\Ncome back and pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:46.98,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to waste my time, so let's go\Nhome after we get to the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:50.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm getting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.93,0:19:52.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:55.02,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Itsuki, but would\Nyou sit in the back?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:58.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,In the back?\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.55,0:20:01.89,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any reason for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.89,0:20:06.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe there is and\Nmaybe there isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.31,0:20:10.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?\NAren't you sure yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:13.04,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I hold my\Nbody during drift?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.04,0:20:14.51,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll... leave it up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.51,0:20:16.26,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Up to me...?  Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.26,0:20:20.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a short ride to the base,\Nso hang in there, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.57,0:20:23.38,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not gonna cancel!\NThere'll be another downhill race!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.38,0:20:26.24,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,The Eight-Six...\NAkina's Eight-Six is gonna race!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.72,0:20:30.24,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, no oncoming traffic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:31.74,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.68,0:20:36.19,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,This is totally unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.19,0:20:38.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but there was nothing we could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.12,0:20:41.69,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Please watch me, Keisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.69,0:20:43.61,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I like rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.61,0:20:51.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Before I joined the team, when I practiced\Ndrifting alone, I chose rainy days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.87,0:20:55.46,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I was poor, so I liked driving in the rain because\Nthe tires didn't wear out so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.46,0:20:59.37,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I like your confidence, but don't\Nunderestimate the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.37,0:21:01.82,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I have more experience in\Nthe rain than anybody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.82,0:21:05.34,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.  If it's raining,\NI have the advantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:09.15,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll win.  The rain is on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.10,0:21:17.25,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takumi, you don't\Nlook very nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:20.61,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright with\Nthis rain battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:22.13,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.13,0:21:25.99,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go as fast in the rain, so I'll\Njust drive like I normally do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.99,0:21:30.50,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I can drive fast or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.50,0:21:32.83,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try not to push myself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.83,0:21:35.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,If I damage the car, Dad'll hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:38.31,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.53,0:21:45.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA0A0A0&}But if he loses, what'll happen to the\Nbattle with Takahashi Ryosuke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.76,0:21:49.76,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll start the countdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.76,0:21:51.01,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Five...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.01,0:21:52.06,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...four...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.06,0:21:53.00,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...three...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.00,0:21:54.12,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...two...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.12,0:21:55.10,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,...one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:55.94,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.21,0:22:26.93,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,YOU CALL THIS NORMAL?!
