Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.26,0:24:32.97,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}A rain battle...\NWill you be alright, Kenta?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.97,0:24:34.57,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I'm confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.57,0:24:37.87,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Keisuke's watching,\Nso I have to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.87,0:24:40.41,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}But your opponent is the Eight-Six,\Nand even Keisuke couldn't beat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.41,0:24:44.33,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want to avenge him!\NIt's for Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.33,0:24:45.66,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}But it's a route you've never\Nraced on before.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.66,0:24:49.79,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be alright.  I'll drive so that\NI won't disgrace Keisuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.79,0:24:53.91,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Wait a minute.  Don't tell me\Nthat Keisuke's your...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.91,0:24:54.65,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.65,0:24:58.08,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Initial D:\N"Downhill Rain Battle!"
