Dialogue: 1,0:24:55.07,0:24:59.98,MainStyle,,0000,0430,0260,,Next Time:
Dialogue: 1,0:24:55.07,0:24:59.98,MainStyle,,0000,0077,0190,,Downhill Rain Battle
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.08,0:24:59.14,MainStyle,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1AFAFF&}Don't miss it.
